headline: Is Intel Stock a Buy Now?
summary: Semiconductor giant Intel (NASDAQ: INTC) is undergoing a tumultuous time in its storied history.  Despite competitors such as Nvidia seeing surging sales amid the artificial intelligence (AI) boom, Intel is struggling.  Sales suffered a 2% year-over-year drop to $53.1 billion for Intel's 2024 fiscal year, ended Dec. 28.
